{"id":586347,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/06/【图说天朝】党管严・雷军爱/","date":"2018-06-07T08:40:55Z","modified":"2018-06-07T08:40:55Z","title":"【图说天朝】党管严・雷军爱","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>小米<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/06/%e3%80%90%e9%ba%bb%e8%be%a3%e6%80%bb%e5%b1%80%e3%80%91%e7%b1%b3%e2%80%a2%e5%85%b1/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">早在2015年就于公司内部成立了党委</a>，是最早参与党建的科技公司之一。当时，董事长雷军站在党旗前致辞的照片很快在网上<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/06/%E3%80%90%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E6%B0%91%E8%AE%AE%E3%80%91%E4%BB%A5%E5%90%8E%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%89%E5%AE%87%E5%AE%99%E7%9C%9F%E7%90%86%E7%81%8C%E9%A1%B6%E5%BC%80%E5%85%89%E8%BF%87%E7%9A%84%E7%B1%B3%E6%89%8D/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">引来大量嘲讽</a>，《环球时报》甚至还发表了文章为之辩护。然而在短短两年后，几乎所有知名的中国科技公司都成立了党支部（党委）。</p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/12/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e7%9f%a5%e4%b9%8e%e5%a7%93%e5%85%9a%ef%bc%9a%e7%a7%81%e4%bc%81%e5%85%9a%e5%bb%ba%e7%83%ad%e7%81%ab%e6%9c%9d%e5%a4%a9%e7%9a%84%e8%83%8c%e5%90%8e/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">【立此存照】知乎姓党：私企党建热火朝天的背后</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/06/%E3%80%90%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E6%B0%91%E8%AE%AE%E3%80%91%E4%BB%A5%E5%90%8E%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%89%E5%AE%87%E5%AE%99%E7%9C%9F%E7%90%86%E7%81%8C%E9%A1%B6%E5%BC%80%E5%85%89%E8%BF%87%E7%9A%84%E7%B1%B3%E6%89%8D/\">【网络民议】以后只有宇宙真理灌顶开光过的米才可以卖</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/06/%e3%80%90%e9%ba%bb%e8%be%a3%e6%80%bb%e5%b1%80%e3%80%91%e7%b1%b3%e2%80%a2%e5%85%b1/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">【麻辣总局】米•共 </a></li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<p>图片来自微博用户 <a href=\"https://weibo.com/canakin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@Anakin</a> ：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_586349\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/雷军的爱.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-586349\"